| 2 | No security headers | High | `helmet` |
| 3 | No rate limiting | High | `express-rate-limit` |
| 4 | No global error handler | Medium | Custom error middleware |
| 5 | No 404 handler | Low | Catch-all middleware |
| 6 | Unauthenticated/unpaginated `/users` | High | Auth middleware + pagination + DTO |
| 7 | Hard-coded port | Low | `process.env.PORT` |
| 8 | No CORS policy | Medium | `cors` with explicit origin allowlist |

